Program 3:Write a program to demonstrate on session and cookies
DESCRIPTION:
In this application demonstrate cookies and sessions through online shopping. First on entering the store, user choices in different 
streams is recorded in the form of a cookie. Then certain books related are displayed on the browser based upon the cookie data.
The user selects some books and add them to his/her cart. At the payment stage, a session is created and will be redirected to a payment
confirmation stage usually a books portal where he/she pays the cart total amount within a stipulated time period to get his/her order
confirmed. Else session expires and redirected to the store. The user is restricted to click the refresh or back button while his/her
session is active. If he/she does so session is invalidated immediately.
